       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL-CALC.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME      PIC X(30).
       01 WS-HOURS-WORKED       PIC 9(3) VALUE 0.
       01 WS-HOURLY-RATE        PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 WS-GROSS-PAY          PIC 9(6)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 WS-TAX-RATE           PIC V99 VALUE .20.
       01 WS-NET-PAY            PIC 9(6)V99 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           MOVE "JANE DOE" TO WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME.
           MOVE 40 TO WS-HOURS-WORKED.
           MOVE 25.00 TO WS-HOURLY-RATE.
           COMPUTE WS-GROSS-PAY = WS-HOURS-WORKED * WS-HOURLY-RATE.
           COMPUTE WS-NET-PAY = WS-GROSS-PAY * (1 - WS-TAX-RATE).
           DISPLAY "EMPLOYEE: " WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME.
           DISPLAY "GROSS PAY: " WS-GROSS-PAY.
           DISPLAY "NET PAY: " WS-NET-PAY.
           STOP RUN.
